    "page_content": "There have been a variety of document data collections to facilitate the development of DL models. Some examples include PRImA [3](magazine layouts), PubLayNet [38](academic paper layouts), Table Bank [18](tables in academic papers), Ne aper Navigator Dataset {I7] (newspaper figure layouts) and HJDataset historical Japanese document layouts). A spectrum of models trained on these datasets are currently available in the LayoutParser model zoo to support different use cases.",
